briefdescription.para: Enumeration representing different character indices for the shgui library.

detaileddescription.para: This enum defines indices for various characters used in the shgui library, including letters, numbers, and special characters.

briefdescription.para: Generate vertex data for a specific character in the shgui library.

detaileddescription.para: This function generates vertex data for a given character, identified by its character index, in the shgui library.

parameterdescription.para: The string representation of the character (not used in the current implementation).
The character index for which to generate vertex data.
Pointer to the raw vertex data destination.

simplesect.para: An integer indicating the success (1) or failure (0) of the operation.

briefdescription.para: Load font data for the ShGui library.

detaileddescription.para: This function loads font data for the ShGui library, initializing necessary resources.

parameterdescription.para: Pointer to the ShGui structure to be initialized with font data.

simplesect.para: An integer indicating the success (1) or failure (0) of the operation.
